Extract the archive to a directory.

In that directory

+-------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                   |
| COPY      libpigpio.a-hard or libpigpio.a-soft to libpigpio.a     |
|                                                                   |
| ACCORDING to whether you have a hard or soft float distribuition. |
|                                                                   |
+-------------------------------------------------------------------+

Enter the following commands (in this order)

make install
make

To test the library do

sudo ./checklib

demolib.c and checklib.c show examples of interfacing with the library.
